api_list.name: Explain Code
api_list.description: Explains a snippet of code in natural language.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://ai-text-to-code-generation.p.rapidapi.com/explain"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "ai-text-to-code-generation.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
